    "name": "Dr. S.C. Kamate",
    "qualification": "M.Tech., Ph.D.",
    "designation": "Principal",
    "message": "Dear Aspirants, I extend a very warm welcome to Hirasugar Institute of Technology, Nidasoshi, Dist: Belgaum, Karnataka. The Institute is located in the rural ambience with a lush green campus spread over on 48 Acres, adjacent to Belgaum-Bijapur Highway. The campus is surrounded by industrial hubs in Manufacturing, Aerospace, Glass, Sugar, IT services and Oil & Natural gas etc., with infinite employment potential. Since inception in 1996, it has produced more than 5000 Alumni serving in Engineering, Management, Technical and Research fields. The success is due to holistic education approach, alumni tracking, continuous evaluation, mentoring, ICT tools, pre-placement training, and GATE/IES preparation. HSIT is a preferred choice for engineering career."
